---

SCOPE

The CC-BY-NC-SA 4.0 license above applies to:
  - paper/                (Wraith paper, ES and EN)
  - paper/charts/         (figures)
  - funding/              (pitch deck and related documents)
  - checkpoint/           (packed 186M Wraith checkpoint)
  - README.md, NOTICE

Source code for the training pipeline (NPQN Training, shadow int16 optimizer,
DSSC/ASR), the GPU inference engine (WraithFastEngine, CUDA kernels, CUDA
Graphs integration), the CPU inference engine (C++ AVX2), and the Dualwire
5-trit/byte packed codec is NOT included in this repository and is NOT
released under this license. Those components are reserved as intellectual
property of the author and are available under separate academic or
commercial licensing terms. See NOTICE for details.

